bookAuthors: Ryan Burton, Adam Gragg, Vinnie Tartamella, Matt Flyer
Plot: Creator of the "Twilight" series, and one of the best-selling authors of our time, Stephenie Meyer is showcased in the pages of "Female Force." Find out how this humble churchgirl from Arizona gained a fan-following of millions by nurturing stories inspired through a vivid dream of romance between a human girl, and a vampire
